mapper: ze探险家.Translation: mapper: ze探险家, EN translation: AllenW @ Ozlin server

我们需要找到并击碎12个面具，才能通向祖达萨.Translation: We need to find and destroy 12 masks to access Zuldazar.

12/12, 10 seconds 魔像即将倒下.Translation: 12/12, 10 seconds, the golem is about to fall.

有一个面具藏在广场最高的柱子上.Translation: There is a mask hidden on the highest pillar of the square.

我们需要找到左右两边的3个按钮才能继续前进.Translation: We need to find 3 buttons on both the left and right sides to proceed.

有一个开关藏在希尔瓦娜斯雕像的后边.Translation: There is a button hidden behind the Sylvanas statue.

击碎面具我们才能通行.Translation: We can only pass by smashing the masks.

门后边的按钮能帮我们提前打开.Translation: The button behind the door can help us open it sooner.

需要找到3个按钮才能打开巨擘封印的大门.Translation: We need to find 3 buttons to open the gate of the Great Seal.

墙已拾取,我们要利用这个爬上巨擘封印.Translation: The wall has been picked up; we will use this to climb up the Great Seal.

吉安娜正在使用大海的力量淹没整个祖达萨！.Translation: Be ware the daughter of the sea! Jaina is using the power of the sea to flood all of Zuldazar!

我们必须赶在巨擘封印被淹没之前逃出去.Translation: We must escape before the Great Seal is submerged.

打败封印的三角龙，我们要用墙搭上去.Translation: Defeat the Trihorn that guards the seal; we will use the wall to get up.

打死王座的三角龙，部落的飞艇会来接我们.Translation: Kill the Trihorn at the throne; the Horde's airship will come to pick us up.

海水已经快涨上来了.Translation: The seawater is about to rise.
